## 8. Conclusion

In autonomous systems, governance cannot rely solely on validating decisions.

Stability depends on constraining the domain in which system dynamics unfold.

The transition from action-level governance to **state-space governance** represents a critical architectural shift for the future of AI systems.

---

## Principle

Governance does not control decisions.

Governance controls the domain in which decisions are allowed to exist.
